translations: v.瞎猜，依推测的估计（guesstimate 的过去式和过去分词）

sentences.sentence: But the second tier of the West is deep and potent enough to rate a mention here, as our voters have guesstimated that seven teams will win 47 or more games.
sentences.translation: 但是西部的第二梯队球队的实力也是不容小觑而值得一提的，我们猜想会有七支球队会至少获得47场以上的胜利。
